snippet.textDisplay: I just ate lunch at Gordon Ramsay Burger a few days ago. Was SERIOUSLY disappointing. The Hell's Kitchen burger was mediocre, nothing special. My table had a dirty knife under it when we sat down. The plates were chipped and very worn. The duck poppers were totally underwhelming. The "View From The Top" burger I ate at the bar in the Stratosphere was much better. Surprising us all, the best part of Ramsay Burger was actually the chicken wings. If I ever decide to go back I'll stick to the wings.
